  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Loitokitok Drought Response</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Development of giant wells for food security, deepening of wells to prevent drying, planting more trees in and around water sources, family planning messages to ensure manageable family size. Install shallow wells, with hand pumps, to ensure safe drinking water for communities, truck water, construct boreholes for diesel fuel extraction.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Loitokitok drought response will focus on addressing the natural disaster concerns of the area, located at the foothills of Mount Kilimanjaro.</narrative>
